



Sr
Fort Cumberland [Md.]10ber [December] the 17 1755



If you will lodge one Hundred pounds in the Hands of Mr Robert Rutherford to Pay for such Necessarys as may be wanted for the Servis I will be accountable for it.1 If Mr Rutherford wants any direction beg you will give such as you think proper & oblige your Most Humble Servant

Thomas Walker

